                     <title key="supplie title">佚名書宋蘇軾洞庭春色賦行書 十二軸</title>
                     <title key="supplie title" xml:lang="en">A set of twelve scrolls featuring calligraphy attributed to Su Shi</title>
                     <author key="Q36020">
                        <persName instant="false" full="yes">蘇軾</persName>
                        <persName type="字" instant="false" full="yes">子瞻</persName>
                        <persName type="字" instant="false" full="yes">和仲</persName>
                        <persName type="號" instant="false" full="yes">東坡居士</persName>
                        <persName type="號" instant="false" full="yes">鐵冠道人</persName>
                        <date notAfter="1200"
                              notBefore="1000"
                              calendar="Gregorian"
                              instant="false">1037-1101</date>
                     </author>
                     <note type="注" anchored="true">The shelfmarks attributed to this set of scrolls do not correspond the text of Dong Ting Chun Se Fu,
                                and the content of each scroll is displayed following the order of shelfmarks.
                                Furthermore, the text written on the scroll does not fully match that of Dong Ting Chun Se Fu.</note>
                     <note type="注" anchored="true">本套立軸由12卷組成，由第二卷落款可知整套為蘇軾 (1037-1101)《洞庭春色賦》的贋品。《洞庭春色賦》與《中山松醪賦》二賦合卷的真跡現藏于中國吉林省博物館，是存世蘇軾書跡中篇幅最長的。
                                Part of the set of twelve scrolls, the text claimed them to be ‘Dong Ting Chun Se Fu’ written by Su Shi (1037-1101). However, these scrolls are not authentic. 
                                The authentic calligraphy of ‘Dong Ting Chun Se Fu’ written by Su Shi is held by the Jilin Museum of China.
                                
                                衣若芬 (2018)。遞藏·題跋·複製：蘇軾《洞庭春色賦》、《中山松醪賦》書跡。《嶺南學報》，復刊 第九輯，頁143-161。檢自 https://commons.ln.edu.hk/ljcs_new/vol9/iss1/8 </note>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (1)</title>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">覺天拄杖遨峰之賦遠離騷也見親家晨光是飄門</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (2)</title>
                        <note type="款識" anchored="true">寄時歸息馬眉山蘇軾書</note>
                        <note type="印章" anchored="true">眉山某蘇軾印</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (3)</title>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">賢王之達觀逸想於人寰焰兮春風天庭之白浪漲北</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (4)</title>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">泡幻藏千里於一斑舉勺罌青綸隨屬車鴟夷木門</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (5)</title>
                        <note type="題目" anchored="true">洞庭春色賦</note>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">吾聞橘中之樂不減商山</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (6)</title>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">記求淺散星宿皋香歲之妙質毛區爛曾和束蒿驚</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (7)</title>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">渚蒼灣佳往游勤鬢鬟命黃千奴震還米之禾三而旌</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (8)</title>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">珠涕沸聲味甘餘之苦姿之高知壞笑非紋樽蟄目</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (9)</title>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">镮兮帝之觴書散江吸神夢始如髦蠻玻色山林屋</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (10)</title>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">醉以授鳥山為我刪松始予濟于衡漳泩而夜燧明</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (11)</title>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">豈霜餘之不食而四老人者游戲於其間悟此世之</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <title type="shelfmark">Backhouse Rolls a. 34 (12)</title>
                        <note type="釋文" anchored="true">其已遠石之軎收用榆製之山松磔通盤出救何艱葉</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <filiation>書法卷軸，中外孤本。</filiation>
